name: Figure IV
description:
Somewhere along the way, I drew two Figure III's but as one wasn't really digitally coloured, I think it is fine to call this Figure IV.

This is part of a series of automatic drawings that all start with a figure study. There is no particular aim behind them, I just find it an interesting diversion from my usual work.

Pen and ink sketch, scanned and coloured in photoshop. Artwork file prints at around 40cm x 60cm.
